		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+0" x="12" type="text"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Be careful counting the zeros in the figures and note that the phrase immediately before the gap is 'up to', so you need to find the maximum age of the ice where the virus was found.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+0" x="12" type="text"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT">&nbsp;</P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
